Subject: Re: [VB] Tranny conversion

Since my pulley is aluminum I just heat the pulley around the center hole 
until it slips on or off. Aluminum pulley expands at a greater rate than the 
steel crank. Works for both installation and removal.

However if you have a stock steel pulley all bets are off.

Chris
